  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Beautician / Beauty Therapist",
  "description": "<p>Love Yourself Because You are Precious! Multi-award winning center, Ceramique Aesthetics Wellness empower and restore confidence by providing skin, body & wellness solutions. Combining cutting-edge technology & natural ingredients, we provide highly effective result driven treatments to our valued customers in our centers. Our products are also available in major e-marketplaces and e-commerce website.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>We are expanding and continuously looking out for talents with growth mindset to join our fun and dynamic team!</strong></p><ul><li>Comprehensive in-house and external training will be provided</li><li>Attractive Basic + Commission structure + incentives + bonus</li><li>Uniforms are provided</li><li>Flexi-work arrangements</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>- Perform full facial, slimming, hair removal and/or wellness treatments for customer</p><p>- Provide basic professional skin or body analysis and consultation</p><p>- Handle customer's enquiries, booking of appointment and receiving customers upon arrival</p><p>- Identify customer’s needs and recommend suitable products and treatments to customer</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Min 2-3 years of related working experience required</p><p>- Candidate who has a beauty/ beautician certified certificate will be an advantage (CIBTAC / CIDESCO / ITEC)</p><p>- Candidate who can start work immediately will be an advantage</p><p>- Team player, passionate to assist customers to achieve their goals</p><p>- Willing to learn, positive working attitude</p><p>- Good interpersonal skills, customer oriented</p><p><br /></p><p>A good employment benefit and good career growth awaits the successful candidate.</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
